T1  - On the dynamics of interstate migration: Migration costs and self-selection
AU  - Bayer, Christian
AU  - Juessen, Falko
JO  - Review of Economic Dynamics
VL  - 15
IS  - 3
SP  - 377
EP  - 401
PY  - 2012
DA  - 2012/07/01/
